bution is the first of its kind internationally to deal\nwith Wikipedia from the point of view of transfer of knowledge on literature to\nthe public. For the theory of this field of research some new aspects are\noffered for debate.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 14 Sep 2015 17:09:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-09-16"}
