ansition disc evolution. In particular, we highlight the\ncurrent lack of explanation for the missing non-accreting transition discs with\nlarge holes, which is a serious issue in the planet hypothesis.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 14 Sep 2015 20:11:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-10-21"}
