. This\nforce can be maintained by the mobile energetic particles streaming upstream of\nthe shocks that, in the most intense events, drive electric currents able to\ngenerate diamagnetic cavities and depressed solar wind density regions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 15 Sep 2015 01:08:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-11-04"}
